messages.id:
🤖 Here is a list of commands that I understand, some of them [may] or (should) contain an argument:
/start - start all over again
/help [other command] - get a list of available commands or help and a demonstration of a specific command
/add [query] - add media from reply to your collection [with custom search query]
/edit (query) - change query to reply media
/del - remove reply media from your collection
